<subSubSection id="40A3DD517446DF2BCE51217DE2A5D81C" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="phenology">
<paragraph id="A3DCE373C725958C1A431173BDD910EF" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Phenology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="37001EAD66DC31E6730F9A8A61653F95" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Flowering and fruiting specimens were collected in July.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="9B536FC0B85210650C215B42BAFAD189" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="CFC21B08D8BCFD11436843A22BF96076" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Distribution and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="75F4E7E1C2A98699CB7139E505354BD3" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">
<taxonomicName id="5C72B770BB7E63AD3D43AECDF591F9A4" authorityName="V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2020" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Helicteres" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Helicteres binhthuanensis" order="Malvales" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="binhthuanensis">
<emphasis id="D6F6DECB98CC385A4D37D036CE579A3A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Helicteres binhthuanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known only from Ham Thuan Bac District, Binh Thuan Province, southern Vietnam. It grows along roadsides and edges of secondary forests at ca. 80-95 m elevation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="6047B7CDEAA3A42F2521A07A80B881F3" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="0F09FB5B6E7C259C8306B72FB34893D0" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BEA9C0EF3DA51338088C942E5AD26FE1" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">The species epithet is derived from the name of the province (Binh Thuan) where the species was discovered.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="DE01144DF9DF863CE6D4A10AC6E9E304" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="vernacular names">
<paragraph id="67BADB33EAFB25B4BA27647E30129DF8" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Vernacular names.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2BBAAE2E4875BAAD73ADE7A2BA34FE0B" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">
Tổ 
<normalizedToken id="326F650DAEE36C5B47FC2269E2F77DDA" originalValue="kén">ken</normalizedToken>
