<subSubSection id="80C375F23C0E7796C9B85B3E461C34AD" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="preliminary conservation assessment">
<paragraph id="03CE4500E6F4A55D62C7EF161B64D7AD" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Preliminary conservation assessment.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="71F15B858C58691D8AA96758A11BA7FE" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">
<taxonomicName id="10E46BC14CED4AB77725CCAF0E57F8A8" authorityName="V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2020" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Helicteres" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Helicteres binhthuanensis" order="Malvales" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="binhthuanensis">
<emphasis id="B8CD41CFC58A1D7104719E8EF1056947" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Helicteres binhthuanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was collected from a small population in a habitat that was logged and disturbed. Therefore, we suggest its placement in the Data Deficient (DD) category based on the IUCN Red List Categories (
<bibRefCitation id="597925E6903355E2036F4A2D840933DA" author="IUCN" journalOrPublisher="Taiwania" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" publicationUrl="http://www.iucnredlist.org/" refId="B7" refString="IUCN, 2019. Guidelines for Using the IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 14. http://www.iucnredlist.org/" title="Guidelines for Using the IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 14." url="http://www.iucnredlist.org/" year="2019">IUCN 2019</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="4797C9B42E6C4241C14BB2C82504B030" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="notes">
<paragraph id="EFDB616729011F87C3ADDB253CE9F86C" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2DAC3CA985712D7387B8C6E7703AEF7A" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">
Morphologically, 
<taxonomicName id="11BAD5AFB2417D526AAC3A91717FFB80" authorityName="V. S. Dang" authorityYear="2020" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Helicteres" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Helicteres binhthuanensis" order="Malvales" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="binhthuanensis">
<emphasis id="CA2A2F5D5F9601B3CE8E862E0F2264F0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Helicteres binhthuanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is most similar to 
<taxonomicName id="F90812E1224CB60F8F08FCBB253A9F5E" genus="H." lsidName="H. angustifolia" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" rank="species" species="angustifolia">
<emphasis id="49D2E8DE0AE66DA4C76AB2524CC2C8FD" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">H. angustifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
